title.narrative: Kosovo Energy Efficiency and Renewable Energy Project

description.narrative: The project development objectives are to: (i) reduce energy consumption and fossil fuel use in public buildings through energy efficiency and renewable energy investments; and (ii) enhance the policy and regulatory environment for renewable energy and energy efficiency.
